descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff00ff][size=4]May I present Medea.  Another token of my appreciation to Nexus Skyrim community.  Her namesake info can be found here: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medea
My hope is that some will enjoy her as much as I enjoyed making her.  Seem to not be able to help myself with doing this for she is now my 5th entry.

[/size][/color][size=3][b]
